>> HELLO, HELLO.

06:21.715 --> 06:22.716
ONE, TWO, THREE.

06:22.841 --> 06:24.218
IS IT -- OH! -- IT IS.

06:24.343 --> 06:28.722
WELCOME, FRIENDS AND FAMILY.

06:28.847 --> 06:31.016
I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE A NICE

06:31.141 --> 06:32.851
TREAT FOR EVERYONE TO

06:32.976 --> 06:35.270
EXPERIENCE CHRISTMAS IN JULY.

