>> WHAT?!

06:36.355 --> 06:38.106
THAT WAS MY IDEA, DAD.

06:38.232 --> 06:39.107
HE CAN'T --

06:39.233 --> 06:41.109
>> NOW'S NOT THE TIME, SON.

06:41.235 --> 06:43.362
>> AND SO I PERSONALLY MADE ALL

